 <span data-ttu-id="99ba2-333">消息队列将消息正文内容视为一个对象或序列化流的形式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="99ba2-333">Message Queuing recognizes the body contents as an object or as a serialized stream.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="99ba2-334"><xref:System.Messaging.Message.BodyType%2A>属性指示的类型中的对象<xref:System.Messaging.Message.Body%2A>消息属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="99ba2-334">The <xref:System.Messaging.Message.BodyType%2A> property indicates the type of the object within the <xref:System.Messaging.Message.Body%2A> property of the message.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="99ba2-335"><xref:System.Messaging.XmlMessageFormatter>消息正文中执行的本机类型和对象之间的绑定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="99ba2-335">The <xref:System.Messaging.XmlMessageFormatter> performs binding between native types and the object in a message body.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="99ba2-336">如果您使用<xref:System.Messaging.XmlMessageFormatter>，则格式化程序设置<xref:System.Messaging.Message.BodyType%2A>为您的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="99ba2-336">If you use the <xref:System.Messaging.XmlMessageFormatter>, the formatter sets the <xref:System.Messaging.Message.BodyType%2A> property for you.</span></span>  
  
